<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/main.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/index.css">
    <title>YourFuture - Página Inicial</title>
</head>

<body>
    <header class="c-header">
        <div class="logo">
            <img id="logo" src="assets/img/Logo.png" alt="" onclick="location.href = '/';" />
        </div>

        <nav id="nav" class="nav-bar">
            <div id="menu-bar" class="menu-items">
                <div id="btnBurger"><span class="iconify" data-icon="fa:bars" style="color: #4b87ff;" data-width="40" data-height="40"> </span> </div>
                <div id="btnCloseBurger"><span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:close" style="color: red;" data-width="40" data-height="40"></span></div>
            </div>

            <ul class="menu">
                <li id="active" class="menu-items">Início</li>
                <li class="menu-items" onclick="location.href = '/academico';">Acadêmico</li>
                <li class="menu-items" onclick="location.href = '/carreira';">Carreira</li>
                <li class="menu-items" onclick="location.href = '/teste';">Teste Vocacional</li>
                <% if (locals.logado) { %>
                    <a href="/logout"> Logado </a>

                    <% } else { %>
                <li class="menu-items"><button onclick="location.href = '/login';" class="menu-button">Entrar</button></li>
                    <% } %>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main class="container">
        <div class="container left">
            <div class="left-container">
                <div class="left-title">
                    <h1>ESTÁ CONFUSO COM</h1>
                    <h3>O SEU FUTURO?</h3>
                </div>
                <p>A YourFuture tem o intuito de auxiliar você a <br />encontrar sua nova profissão ou graduação.<br /> Você irá perder essa chance? Um futuro <br />brilhante está a um click de você.</p>
                <button class="left-button">Saiba Mais</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container right">
            <img src="assets/img/Vetor-Woman-Run.png" alt="" />
        </div>

    </main>

    <div class="change-theme-container change-theme-button">
        <span class="iconify" data-icon="fluent:dark-theme-24-filled" data-width="22px" style=" color: var(--text); "></span>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.iconify.design/2/2.0.3/iconify.min.js "></script>
    <script type="text/javascript " src="burguerdrop.js "></script>
    <script type="text/javascript " src="theme-toggle.js "></script>

</body>

</html>